## Append-only narrative logs — prettier's markdown formatter mangles bare `_` / `*`
## inside one-line entries (e.g. `node_modules` → `node*modules`, `synth_*` → `synth*\*`),
## which corrupts already-shipped historical lines on every run. Keep these byte-for-byte.
